# 🇮🇳 PingCrowds Lab — India Map Simulator

### Learn by Seeing. Explore by Experiencing.

Welcome to the **India Map Simulator**, an experimental project from **PingCrowds Lab**.

This project explores a simple idea:

> Learning becomes more powerful when we can see, interact, and experience information.

The simulator helps students explore India visually through maps and interactive experiments.

Instead of only reading facts, students can observe, discover patterns, and build curiosity through exploration.

---

## 🌱 Project Status

This is an evolving lab experiment.

The simulator is not a complete system yet. New ideas, map layers, visualizations, and learning experiences will be added gradually over time.

The goal is to keep improving through experimentation.

